    {
      "id": "PopularPost276274",
      "post_content": "At first I thought this would be highly rated...  \nUntil I noticed the comments, and that this costs TWO more, not one more, than [Absorb](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Absorb), and how significant CMC really is.  \n  \nI think this card would have been Epic to see at {W}{W}{U}{U}. 4 CMC, it gains you more life than [Absorb](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Absorb), it should cost more, Wizards is now printing most hard counters to cost at least UU (as in, at least 2-weight blue, PLUS whatever colorless or other mana), and {1}{W}{U}{U} is seemingly not where Wizards wants the power level of counterspells sitting at this time.  \n  \nI think this card might only just barely not be very oppressive at {W}{U}{U}, but it would be a near miss, and Wizards just doesn't take that kind of risks with Counterspells because the gameplay consequences really are too unfun when Counters are too strong.",
      "posted_by": "DarthParallax",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost276274\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">At first I thought this would be highly rated...<br/>Until I noticed the comments, and that this costs TWO more, not one more, than <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Absorb\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Absorb\">Absorb</a>, and how significant CMC really is.<br/><br/>I think this card would have been Epic to see at {W}{W}{U}{U}. 4 CMC, it gains you more life than <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Absorb\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Absorb\">Absorb</a>, it should cost more, Wizards is now printing most hard counters to cost at least UU (as in, at least 2-weight blue, PLUS whatever colorless or other mana),  and {1}{W}{U}{U} is seemingly not where Wizards wants the power level of counterspells sitting at this time.<br/><br/>I think this card might only just barely not be very oppressive at {W}{U}{U}, but it would be a near miss, and Wizards just doesn't take that kind of risks with Counterspells because the gameplay consequences really are too unfun when Counters are too strong.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '276274'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy46041\">DarthParallax</span>\r\n                                (10/14/2012 5:08:56 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>"
